com.vmware.vapi.provider

Interface ApiInterface

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    ActivationManagerApiInterface, ActivationManagerSyncApiInterface, com.vmware.vapi.internal.bindings.ApiInterfaceSkeleton, ApiMethodBasedApiInterface, OperationApiInterface, OperationSyncApiInterface, ProviderApiInterface, ProviderSyncApiInterface, ServiceApiInterface, ServiceSyncApiInterface

    public interface ApiInterface
    The ApiInterface interface provides introspection APIs for a vAPI interface; it is implemented by API providers.
